e%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwarappa%20said%20his%20fight%20is%20against%20the%20control%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20%26quot%3Bby%20one%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20used%20to%20say%20that%20Congress%20has%20a%20family%20culture.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20one%20family%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20should%20be%20freed%20from%20that%20family.%20Party%20workers%20are%20hurt.%20I%20will%20compete%20and%20contest%20to%20relieve%20the%20pain%20of%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20work%20of%20those%20who%20fought%20for%20Hindutva%20ideology%20and%20the%20organization%20should%20be%20respected.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20contesting%20to%20fix%20the%20mess.%20I%20will%20not%20step%20back%20from%20the%20decision%2C%20I%20will%20pay%20my%20respects%20to%20you%20and%20come%20to%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEshwarappa%20said%20his%20son%20had%20told%20him%20that%20even%20if%20he%20does%20not%20get%20a%20political%20future%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20party%20should%20be%20cleansed%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Karnataka%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20phases%20on%20April%2026%20and%20May%207%20for%2028%20constituencies.%20Shivamogga%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712206980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2F2clufu68_ks-eshwarappa-twitter-650-_650x400_13_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-bjp-leader-ks-eshwarappa-fails-to-meet-amit-shah-announces-independent-fight-5371232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Karnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20