0Delhi%20Capitals%20Stars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20106-run%20loss%20to%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20match%2C%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20head%20coach%20Ricky%20Ponting%20said%20that%20he%20was%20embarrassed%20with%20his%20side's%20first%20half%20of%20the%20game%20and%20how%20his%20side%20conceded%20too%20many%20runs%20while%20bowling%20at%20a%20slow-over%20rate.%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20produced%20a%20remarkable%20performance%20in%20all%20facets%20of%20the%20game%20against%20Delhi%20Capitals%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20at%20the%20ACA-VDCA%20Cricket%20Stadium%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20match%20in%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%2C%20Ponting%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20almost%20embarrassed%20with%20our%20first%20half%20of%20the%20game%20today%20-%20to%20concede%20that%20many%20runs.%20It%20took%20us%20two%20hours%20as%20well%20to%20bowl%20our%20overs%2C%20so%20we%20were%20two%20overs%20behind%20again%2C%20which%20means%20the%20guys%20bowling%20the%20last%20two%20overs%20only%20get%20to%20bowl%20with%20four%20fielders%20outside%20the%20circle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20that%20happened%20in%20this%20game%20that%20are%20unacceptable%3B%20we%20have%20to%20fix%20%5Bthem%5D%20immediately%20to%20go%20forward%20in%20this%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20Australian%20skipper%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPonting%20said%20that%20KKR%20were%20relentless%20throughout%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20got%20off%20to%20a%20flying%20start%20in%20the%20powerplay.%20They%20were%20around%2090%20runs%20after%20six%20overs.%20That%20phase%20is%20not%20ideal%3B%20if%20that%20happens%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20game%2C%20then%20you%20are%20always%20trying%20to%20find%20your%20way%20back%20into%20the%20game%20and%20they%20di