.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpag-backed-nuvama-eyes-middle-east-for-400-million-for-first-time-124040400159_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpag-backed-nuvama-eyes-middle-east-for-400-million-for-first-time-124040400159_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Teacher%20Who%20Raped%20Student%20With%20Her%20Partner%20Banned%20From%20Teaching%20For%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20teacher%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20raping%20a%20child%20while%20serving%20as%20deputy%20head%20at%20a%20primary%20school%20has%20been%20permanently%20barred%20from%20returning%20to%20the%20teaching%20profession%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20BBC.%3C%2Fem%3E%20Julie%20Morris%2C%20now%2046%20years%20old%2C%20held%20the%20position%20of%20'safeguarding%20lead'%20at%20St%20George's%20Central%20Primary%20School%20in%20Tyldesley%2C%20near%20Wigan%2C%20when%20she%20engaged%20in%20acts%20of%20'grave%20sexual%20depravity'%20with%20her%20mechanic%20boyfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Morris%20was%20convicted%20and%20sentenced%2C%20her%20case%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20Teaching%20Regulation%20Agency%20(TRA)%2C%20responsible%20for%20handling%20misconduct%20cases.%20A%20three-person%20panel%20was%20convened%20on%20February%2019%20of%20this%20year%20to%20review%20her%20case.%20At%20Morris'%20request%2C%20the%20proceedings%20were%20conducted%20without%20a%20public%20hearing%20and%20without%20Morris%20being%20present%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-merseyside-68716990%5C%22%3Ethe%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20concluded%20that%20Morris'%20actions%20were%20'fundamentally%20incompatible%20with%20her%20being%20a%20teacher%2C'%20leading%20to%20her%20permanent%20ban%20from%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel's%20report%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20Ms%20Morris%20was%20also%20the%20safeguarding%20lead%20at%20her%20school%20makes%20her%20offence%20all%20the%20more%20shocking%20in%20that%2C%20while%20the%20designated%20point%20of%20contact%20for%20welfare%20and%20safety%20concerns%20at%20the%20school%2C%20she%20herself%20was%20engaged%20in%20abusing%20a%20child%2C%20albeit%20not%20one%20at%20the%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20a%20real%20risk%20of%20Ms%20Morris%20repeating%20her%20offending%20behaviour%26quot%3B%20and%20noted%20that%20her%20actions%20were%20%26quot%3Bdeliberate%20and%20sustained%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20that%20she%20was%20acting%20under%20duress.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDavid%20Oatley%2C%20who%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20prohibit%20her%20from%20teaching%2C%20added%20in%20his%20report%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20allegations%20found%20proved%20against%20her%2C%20I%20have%20decided%20that%20Ms%20Morris%20shall%20not%20be%20entitled%20to%20apply%20for%20restoration%20of%20her%20eligibility%20to%20teach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712204040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgmu1d67o_julie-morris-and-david-morris_625x300_04_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-teacher-who-raped-a-student-with-her-partner-banned-from-teaching-for-life-5371107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20school%20teacher%2C%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20sexually%20assaulting%20a%20child%2C%20has%20been%20permanently%20barred%20from%20working%20in%20education.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-teacher-who-raped-a-student-with-her-partner-banned-from-teaching-for-life-5371107%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbritish-teacher-who-raped-a-student-with-her-partner-banned-from-teaching-for-life-5371107%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%2