%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2020%20crore%2C%20but%20owns%20no%20vehicle%20or%20residential%20flat%2C%20according%20to%20his%20affidavit%20to%20file%20nomination%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20declared%20about%20Rs%209.24%20crore%20in%20movable%20assets.%20This%20includes%20Rs%2055%2C000%20cash%2C%20Rs%2026.25%20lakh%20in%20bank%20deposits%2C%20Rs%204.33%20crore%20in%20bonds%20and%20shares%2C%20Rs%203.81%20crore%20in%20mutual%20funds%2C%20Rs%2015.21%20lakh%20in%20gold%20bonds%20and%20jewellery%20worth%20Rs%204.20%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20owns%20immoveable%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2011.15%20crore.%20These%20include%20agricultural%20land%20in%20Delhi's%20Mehrauli%20that%20he%20co-owns%20with%20sister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20also%20owns%20office%20space%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20currently%20valued%20at%20over%20Rs%209%20crore.%20While%20the%20agricultural%20land%20has%20been%20mentioned%20as%20inherited%20property%2C%20the%20office%20space%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20has%20also%20detailed%20in%20the%20affidavit%20the%20police%20cases%20he%20faces.%20These%20include%20a%20case%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%20(POCSO)%20for%20allegedly%20disclosing%20the%20identity%20of%20family%20members%20of%20a%20rape%20victim%20in%20a%20social%20media%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20said%20that%20as%20per%20directions%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20FIR%20is%20in%20a%20sealed%20cover.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20FIR.%20I%20am%20also%20not%20aware%20of%20whether%20I%20am%20arraigned%20as%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20FIR.%20I%20am%2C%20however%2C%20disclosing%20its%20existence%20out%20of%20abundant%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20cases%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%20include%20those%20filed%20on%20complaints%20of%20defamation%20by%20BJP%20leaders.%20He%20has%20also%20mentioned%20in%20his%20affidavit%20the%20criminal%20conspiracy%20case%20linked%20to%20Associated%20Journals%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20won%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%202019%20general%20election.%20This%20time%2C%20he%20is%20up%20against%20CPI%20leader%20Annie%20Raja%20and%20state%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Surendran%20in%20the%20high-profile%20contest%20scheduled%20for%20April%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712201820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F6f2b1q5_rahul-gandhi-nomination_625x300_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-20-crore-assets-land-shared-with-priyanka-gurugram-office-5371077%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2020%20crore%2C%20but%20owns%20no%20vehicle%20or%20residential%20flat%2C%20according%20to%20his%20affidavit%20to%20file%20nomination%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-20-crore-assets-land-shared-with-priyanka-gurugram-office-5371077%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-20-crore-assets-land-shared-with-priyanka-gurugram-office-5371077%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-rahul-gandhis-20-crore-assets-land-shared-with-priyanka-gurugram-office-5371077%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Salman%20is%20not%20filing%20a%20case%20against%20Kunal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712201303000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109020781%2Cimgsize-14736.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22