-army-gaza%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoint%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20%2B972%20Magazine%2C%20a%20Tel%20Aviv-based%20outlet%2C%20and%20Local%20Call%20unveiled%20some%20of%20the%20methodology%20behind%20the%20IDF's%20targeting%20of%20Hamas%20and%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20militants%20in%20Gaza%20based%20on%20interviews%20with%20six%20Israeli%20intelligence%20officers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Fapr%2F03%2Fisrael-gaza-ai-database-hamas-airstrikes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20also%20provided%20exclusive%20access%20to%20the%20testimonies%20from%20the%20six%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%2C%20who%20remained%20unnamed%2C%20told%20the%20outlets%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIDF%20used%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20system%20internally%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BLavender%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20order%20to%20create%20a%20database%20of%20potential%20targets%20who%20may%20be%20linked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-hamas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20PIJ.%20At%20one%20point%20during%20the%20early%20weeks%20of%20the%20war%2C%20the%20system%20identified%20up%20to%2037%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20according%20to%20four%20of%20the%20intelligence%20sources%2C%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20AI%20identified%20a%20potential%20target%2C%20a%20human%20would%20devote%20less%20than%20a%20minute%20to%20check%20the%20machine's%20decision%2C%20a%20source%20told%20the%20outlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20invest%2020%20seconds%20for%20each%20target%20at%20this%20stage%20and%20do%20dozens%20of%20them%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20intelligence%20source%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Guardian.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20zero%20added%20value%20as%20a%20human%2C%20apart%20from%20being%20a%20stamp%20of%20approval.%20It%20saved%20a%20lot%20of%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20AI-based%20targeting%20system%2C%20especially%20early%20in%20the%20war%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20IDF%20made%20it%20permissible%20to%20kill%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20civilians%20for%20every%20suspected%20Hamas%20militant%20assassinated%2C%20two%20of%20the%20sources%20told%20%2B972%20and%20Local%20Call.%20In%20warfare%2C%20these%20civilian%20deaths%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20collateral%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20sources%20told%20the%20outlets%20that%20in%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20of%20the%20war%2C%20the%20IDF%20allowed%20up%20to%2015%20or%2020%20civilian%20deaths%20for%20every%20low-ranking%20Hamas%20militant%20assassinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20number%20could%20increase%20to%20up%20to%20more%20than%20100%20civilians%20if%20the%20IDF%20were%20targeting%20a%20single%20senior%20Hamas%20official%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20completely%20permissive%20policy%20regarding%20the%20casualties%20of%20operations%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20source%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20%26quot%3BA%20policy%20so%20permissive%20that%20in%20my%20opinion%20it%20had%20an%20element%20of%20revenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20allowed%20collateral%20damage%20has%20fluctuated%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20war%2C%20with%20one%20intelligence%20officer%20saying%20the%20rate%20was%20recently%20brought%20down%20again%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20IDF%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20The%20Guardian%20as%20well%20as%20%2B972%20and%20Local%20Call%2C%20an%20IDF%20spokesperson%20denied%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20kill%20list%20containing%20thousands%