some%20things%20you%20can't%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxar%20Patel%2C%20the%20lone%20spinner%20in%20the%20DC%20team%2C%20bowled%20only%20one%20over%20that%20yielded%2018%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSee%20the%20thought%20process%20was%20that%20we%20didn't%20want%20to%20use%20spinners%20but%20our%20fast%20bowlers%20were%20going%20through%20the%20motions.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20time%20for%20reflection%20as%20an%20individual.%20We%20need%20to%20learn%20from%20these%20mistakes%20and%20come%20out%20positive%20in%20the%20next%20match.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%2C%20who%20is%20coming%20off%20a%20long%20layoff%2C%20himself%20looked%20in%20fine%20touch%20as%20he%20scored%20his%20second%20consecutive%20fifty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoing%20fine.%20Getting%20out%20there.%20Enjoying%20every%20day%20but%20cricket%20has%20its%20own%20ups%20and%20downs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayer%20of%20the%20Match%20Narine%20who%20notched%20his%20highest%20T20%20score%20said%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20contribute%20with%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCricket%20is%20all%20about%20batting%20so%20looking%20to%20contribute%20more%20as%20a%20batter.%20That%20said%2C%20I%20still%20enjoy%20by%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20team%20joke%20that%20he%20does%20not%20attend%20batting%20meetings%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20one%20role%20and%20the%20less%20I%20know%20the%20better%20it%20is%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20it%20is%20what%20the%20team%20needs.%20If%20they%20need%20me%20to%20bat%2C%20I%20will%20bat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWinning%20captain%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20was%20lavish%20in%20his%20praise%20for%20Narine%20and%20young%20Angkrish%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20who%20both%20scored%20blazing%20half-centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20I%20said%20in%20the%20toss%20interview%2C%20Sunny%20is%20there%20to%20take%20on%20the%20bowlers%2C%20and%20if%20he