20ended%20up%20suffering%20a%20106-run%20defeat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pace%20duo%20of%20Mitchell%20Starc%20and%20Vaibhav%20Arora%20bagged%20two%20wickets%20each%20to%20reduce%20DC%20to%2033%2F4%20in%20the%20powerplay.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20blow%20derailed%20DC's%20approach%20to%20chasing%20down%20the%20massive%20total%20which%20got%20more%20challenging%20with%20each%20delivery.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(55)%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs%20(54)%20bought%20up%20a%2093-run%20stand%20with%20some%20effortless%20power%20hitting%20and%20gave%20the%20home%20fans%20something%20to%20cheer%20about.%20'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPant%20scored%20back-to-back%20half-centuries%20in%20the%20IPL%20showcasing%20signs%20of%20him%20returning%20to%20his%20prime%20form.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20Pant's%20dismissal%2C%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%20for%20DC%20as%20they%20ended%20up%20losing%20the%20game%20with%20a%20massive%20margin%20of%20106%20runs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKKR%20marched%20on%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20table%20with%20their%20third%20consecutive%20win%20of%20the%20campaign.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20innings%2C%20the%20'City%20of%20Destiny'%20witnessed%20two%20hours%20of%20carnage%2C%202%20hours%20of%20ruthless%20ball-striking%20and%20120%20minutes%20of%20torture%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(DC)%20bowlers%20as%20Narine%20(85)%2C%20Raghuvanshi%20(54)%2C%20Russell%20(41)%20and%20Rinku%20Singh's%20brutal-bashing%20helped%20KKR%20come%20within%20touching%20distance%20of%20surpassing%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20score%20of%20277%2C%20however%20Kolkata%20ended%20up%20with%20the%20second-highest%20total%20in%20the%20IPL%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20winning%20the%20toss%20and%20opting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20KKR%20got%20off%20to%20a%20rollicking%20start%20with%20a%20fiery%20partnership%20between%20Philip%20Salt%20and%20Sunil%20Narine.%20Having%20not%20grabbed%20a