e%20mood%20on%20the%20other.%20The%20duo%20completed%20their%20100-run%20partnership%20with%20significant%20ease.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20phenomenal%20Narine%20innings%20came%20to%20an%20end%2C%20much%20to%20the%20ultimate%20relief%20of%20the%20DC%20bowling%20unit%20until%20Marsh%20got%20the%20big%20wicket.%20Narine%20went%20back%20to%20the%20pavilion%20after%20scoring%2085%20off%20just%2039%20balls.%20Nortje%20sent%20Raghuvanshi%20packing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaghuvanshi%20rocked%20up%20on%20debut%20and%20delivered%20a%20stunning%20performance%20of%2054%20off%2027%20however%20his%20fine%20knock%20came%20to%20an%20end%20as%20he%20was%20sent%20packing%20by%20Nortje%20in%20the%2013.2%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2015%20overs%20into%20the%20match%2C%20KKR%20crossed%20the%20200%20mark.%20In%20the%20second-last%20over%20of%20the%20game%2C%20Rinku%20Singh%20smoked%20Nortje%20for%20three%20maximums%20and%20one%20four%20before%20losing%20his%20wicket%20to%20a%20miss-timed%20shot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20terrific%20yorker%20from%20Ishant%20dismissed%20Russell%2C%20rattling%20off%20the%20wickets%20with%20a%20fiery%20pace.%20In%20the%20same%20over%20he%20removed%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20putting%20a%20stop%20to%20KKR's%20dominant%20performance%2C%20restricting%20Kolkata%20to%20272%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712197680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fuptrbs6g_sca_625x300_03_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Ffirst-time-ever-in-ipl-history-kkrs-mammoth-272-scripts-momentous-record-5369071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20registered%20a%20mammoth%20total%20of%20272%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20seven%20wickets%20against%20Delhi%20Capitals%20in%20IPL%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22amp