marketing%20my%20whole%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20a%20company%20in%20the%20software%20space%20for%20four%20years%20when%20the%20company%20did%20a%20round%20of%20layoffs.%20I%20survived%20the%20cut%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20team%20was%20let%20go%20and%20the%20job%20didn't%20feel%20the%20same.%20I%20was%20opening%20up%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20new%20roles%20when%20the%20perfect%20opportunity%20presented%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20manager%20from%20another%20company%20in%20the%20same%20industry%20reached%20out%20and%20made%20me%20a%20job%20offer%20I%20could%20not%20refuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20the%20offer.%20Shortly%20after%20I%20joined%2C%20new%20leadership%20was%20brought%20in%20at%20the%20C-suite%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202023%2C%20close%20to%20my%2060-day%20mark%2C%20the%20company%20laid%20off%2030%25%20of%20its%20staff.%20My%20entire%20team%2C%20including%20my%20manager%20and%20I%2C%20were%20let%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20shock%20because%20the%20company%20had%20put%20in%20so%20much%20effort%20to%20poach%20me%2C%20make%20an%20attractive%20offer%2C%20and%20spend%20time%20onboarding%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20naive%20and%20silly.%20I%20had%20just%20announced%20my%20job%20move%20to%20my%20whole%20network%20and%20told%20them%20all%20about%20my%20new%20responsibilities.%20There%20were%20practical%20worries%20too%3A%20I%20had%20just%20set%20up%20my%20insurance%20and%20had%20asked%20for%20my%20401K%20to%20be%20rolled%20over.%20My%20entire%20team%20being%20fired%20also%20made%20me%20question%20my%20abilities%20and%20how%20this%20looked%20from%20the%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJob%20search%20struggles%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20collected%20myself%2C%20I%20went%20on%20to%20LinkedIn%20and%20let%20people%20know%20I%20had%20been%20let%20go%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20new%20opportunities.%20I%20also%20began%20applying%20for%20jobs%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20was%20open-minded%20about%20roles%20and