%20under%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-trader-joes-is-so-cheap-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprivate%20labeling%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Trader%20Joe's%20doesn't%20make%20those%20deals%20public%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20easy%20to%20guess%20what%20a%20product%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdupe%26quot%3B%20of.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eater.com%2F2017%2F8%2F9%2F16099028%2Ftrader-joes-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEater%3C%2Fa%3E%20analyzed%20FDA%20recalls%20to%20uncover%20which%20name%20brand%20made%20a%20white-labeled%20Trader%20Joe's%20version.%20As%20of%20Eater's%20analysis%20in%202017%3A%20Stacy's%20pita%20chips%20also%20made%20the%20Trader%20Joe's%20pita%20chips%2C%20Naked%20made%20their%20green%20juice%2C%20Tribe%20made%20the%20classic%20hummus%2C%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Taste%20report%2C%20in%20certain%20cases%2C%20Trader%20Joe's%20has%20shown%20interest%20in%20a%20small%20brand%2C%20asked%20for%20samples%20and%20more%20information%20under%20the%20premise%20of%20doing%20a%20deal%20with%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20turned%20around%20and%20made%20a%20highly%20similar%20product%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20company%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrooklyndelhi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrooklyn%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20makes%20jarred%20Indian%20sauces%20believes%20Trader%20Joe's%20copied%20one%20of%20its%20signature%20sauces%20after%20a%20private%20labeling%20deal%20fell%20through.%20Another%20small%20brand%2C%20Auria's%20Malaysian%20Kitchen%2C%20claims%20a%20similar%20thing%20happened%20to%20them%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EAccording%20to%20%5BAuria%5D%20Abraham%2C%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20deal%20required%20her%20to%20partner%20with%20a%20specific%20co-packer%20(a%20third%20party%20that%20handles%20the%20manufacturing)%20based%20in%20California.%20Abraham%20exchanged%20several%20calls%20and%20emails%20with%20the%20co-packer%20in%20late%202019%2C%20but%20the%20financial%20terms%20were%20onerous%2C%20leaving%20Abraham%20feeling%20uneasy%20about%20a%20potential%20partnership.%20In%20return%20for%20private%20labeling%20her%20product%20for%20Trader%20Joe's%2C%20she%20was%20told%20she%20would%20receive%20a%20modest%20finder's%20fee%20based%20on%20the%20co-packer's%20profits%E2%80%94not%20a%20percentage%20of%20Trader%20Joe's%20sales.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EAfter%20sharing%20samples%20with%20the%20co-packer%20and%20sending%20a%20counteroffer%20asking%20for%20greater%20transparency%2C%20she%20never%20heard%20back%20from%20him%20or%20from%20Trader%20Joe's.%20Within%20a%20matter%20of%20months%2C%20Trader%20Joe's%20released%20a%20product%20with%20a%20similar%20recipe%20and%20flavor%20profile%20that%20it%20called%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.traderjoes.com%2Fhome%2Fproducts%2Fpdp%2Fthai-style-green-chili-sauce-070199%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThai-Style%20Green%20Chili%20Sauce%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20sauce%20was%20also%20made%20with%20jalape%C3%B1o%20and%20Auria's%20signature%20sambal%20ingredient%2C%20makrut%20lime%20leaves%20(Trader%20Joe's%20labeled%20them%20as%20%26quot%3BThai%20lime%20leaves%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20product's%20jar).%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20brand%20owners%20said%20that%20Trader%20Joe's%20tactics%20were%20unlike%20Costco%20or%20other%20big%20chains%20that%20do%20private%20labeling.%20One%20brand%20owner%2C%20who%20thinks%20that%20Trader%20Joe's%20copied%20their%20hummus%20with%20chili%20crisp%20topping%20snack%2C%20compared%20the%20grocer%20to%20fast-fashion%20brands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-shein-billion-dollar-fast-fashion-company-explained-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShein%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Zara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrader%20Joe's%20told%20Taste%2C%20in%20response%20to%20qu