2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20interest%20rate%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-high-yield-savings-accounts-rates-right-now%5C%22%3Ehigh-yield%20savings%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20fluctuated%20quite%20a%20bit.%20Whenever%20I%20see%20that%20the%20rates%20are%20higher%20with%20CDs%2C%20and%20the%20terms%20aren't%20longer%20than%2018%20months%20(since%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20have%20access%20to%20the%20money%20if%20I%20need%20it%20in%20the%20short%20term)%2C%20I'll%20move%20a%20chunk%20of%20my%20cash%20into%20a%20CD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20for%20example%2C%20my%20bank%20sent%20me%20an%20offer%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-18-month-cd-rates%5C%22%3E18-month%20CD%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20interest%20rate%20that%20was%20one%20full%20percentage%20point%C2%A0higher%20than%20the%20rate%20offered%20at%20that%20point%20on%20my%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%20I'm%20currently%20assessing%20how%20much%20cash%20I'm%20willing%20to%20put%20into%20this%20CD%20and%20not%20touch%20it%20for%20that%20time%20period%20in%20order%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20better%20interest%20rate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20When%20a%20CD%20matures%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20any%20given%20time%20during%20the%20year%2C%20I%20have%20as%20many%20as%20three%20CD%20accounts%20open%20and%20in%20use.%20Usually%2C%20at%20least%20once%20a%20year%2C%20the%20money%20in%20that%20CD%20matures%2C%20which%20means%20I'm%20able%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20withdraw%20the%20cash%20or%20renew%20the%20CD%20for%20the%20same%20term%2C%20though%20the%20interest%20rate%20might%20have%20changed%20(either%20higher%20or%20lower).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20if%20the%20APY%20offered%20in%20my%20high-yield%20savings%20account%20is%20higher%2C%20I'll%20move%20the%20cash%20back%20into%20that%20account%20to%20earn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-compound-interest%5C%22%3Ecompound%20interest%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20leave%20it%20there%20or%20hunt%20for%20another%20high-interest%20CD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20When%20an%20influx%20of%20cash%20can%20be%20left%20alone%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20my%20income%20often%20varies.%20I%20live%20on%20a%20strict%20budget%20that%20helps%20me%20manage%20my%20spending%20and%20put%20aside%20money%20every%20month%20to%20help%20me%20reach%20my%20financial%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20get%20an%20influx%20of%20cash%20from%20a%20new%20project%20or%20a%20product%20I%20created%20that%20generates%20a%20lot%20of%20profit%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20with%20a%20chunk%20of%20money%20that%20I%20can%20put%20aside%20and%20not%20touch%20for%20a%20while.%20That's%20when%20I'll%20hunt%20for%20a%20CD%20that%20offers%20the%20highest%20interest%20rate%20that%20I%20can%20find%2C%20for%20the%20time%20period%20that%20I'm%20willing%20to%20leave%20the%20money%20untouched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20not%20sure%20whether%20or%20not%20I%20can%20keep%20the%20cash%20in%20a%20longer-term%20CD%2C%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20risk%20having%20to%20pay%20early%20withdrawal%20penalties%2C%20I'll%20search%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-no-penalty-cds%5C%22%3Eno-penalty%20CD%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20When%20I%20need%20to%20access%20the%20cash%20for%20other%20opportunities%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20I%20invest%20in%20new%20streams%20of%20passive%20income%2C%20whether%20that's%20putting%20the%20money%20into%20REITs%20or%20creating%20a%20new%20product%20to%20sell%20to%20my%20audience%20(such%20as%20an%20online%20course).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDepending%20on%20the%20interest%20rates%20available%2C%20I%20might%20have%20more%20cash%20in%20CDs%20than%20in%20my%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%20But%20when%20I%20know%20that%20in%20the%20near%20future%20I'll%20need%20some%20of%20the%20cash%20to%20invest%20in%20other%20passive%20income%20streams%2C%20I%20make%20sure%20to%20move%20money%20out%20of%20the%20no-penalty%20CDs%20I%20have%20into%20my%20high-yield%20savings%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-no-penalty-cds%5C%22%3Ebest%20no-penalty%20CDs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20good%20way%20to%20lock%20in%20higher%20rates%20on%20CDs%20without%20facing%20penalties%20if%20you%20need%20to%20withdraw%20funds%20before%20the%20maturity%20date.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcit-bank-cd-rates%5C%22%3ECIT%20Bank%20CD%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fraisin-review%5C%22%3ERaisin%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20popular%20no-penalty%20CD%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20October%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-money-between-savings-accounts-cds-2024-04%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712181301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F634d5ee56bd527001914e936%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-money-between-savings-accounts-cds-2024-04%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20interest%20rates%20fluctuate%2C%20she%20chases%20the%20highest%20APY%20by%20moving%20her%20money%20between%20high-yield%20savings%20accounts%20and%20CDs%20to%20earn%20the%20most%20on%20her%20savings.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-money-bet