0relationships%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGagne%20got%20married%20to%20David%2C%20her%20childhood%20sweetheart.%20Together%2C%20they%20share%20two%20children%2C%20a%20dog%2C%20and%20a%20cat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20passionate%20mother%20and%20wife%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%20in%20the%20book.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20an%20engaging%20therapist.%20I%20am%20extremely%20charming%20and%20well-liked.%20I%20have%20lots%20of%20friends.%20I%20am%20a%20member%20of%20a%20country%20club.%20I%20throw%20parties%20for%20every%20occasion%20you%20can%20imagine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20been%20able%20to%20have%20lasting%20relationships%20with%20her%20friends%20and%20family%20because%20she%20sought%20treatment%20and%20answers%2C%20which%20is%20why%20she%20pursued%20her%20PhD%20and%20started%20publicly%20speaking%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20her%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20a%20twenty-first-century%20sociopath%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I've%20written%20this%20book%20because%20I%20know%20I'm%20not%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-people-get-wrong-about-sociopath-according-to-sociopathic-therapist-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712180219000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660d9b071caec1275a6c74ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-people-get-wrong-about-sociopath-according-to-sociopathic-therapist-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr.%20Patric%20Gagne%20is%20a%20diagnosed%20sociopath%20and%20received%20a%20PhD%20in%20psychology%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20sociopathy.%20She%20wrote%20a%20memoir%20about%20her%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpugachevsky%40insider.com%20(Julia%20Pugachevsky)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-pe