ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-sprinkler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20best%20sprinklers%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20range%20of%20sprinkler%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20watering%20can%3Cp%3EFor%20smaller%20gardens%2C%20window%20boxes%2C%20and%20even%20houseplants%2C%20a%20watering%20can%20might%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20supply%20your%20plants%20with%20the%20water%20they%20crave.%20But%20some%20plants%20require%20a%20gentle%20sprinkle%20so%20as%20not%20to%20crush%20leaves%20or%20delicate%20blooms.%20Other%2C%20hardier%20plants%20may%20need%20a%20larger%20volume%20of%20water%20more%20easily%20delivered%20in%20a%20steady%20stream.%20The%20Bloem%20Easy%20Pour%20Watering%20Can%C2%A0has%20a%20rotating%20head%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20deliver%20the%20proper%20stream%20to%20your%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20large%20watering%20can%20with%20a%202.6-gallon%20capacity%2C%20and%20anyone%20who's%20hauled%20water%20across%20their%20lawn%20to%20their%20plants%20can%20attest%20to%20how%20heavy%20water%20gets.%20These%20larger%20cans%20can%20be%20tough%20to%20pour%2C%20putting%20a%20strain%20on%20your%20arms%20and%20wrists.%20Bloem%20has%20taken%20that%20into%20consideration%20as%20well.%20Its%20double%20grip%20allows%20you%20to%20place%20your%20hand%20however%20you'll%20get%20the%20most%20leverage.%20You%20can%20also%20grip%20with%20two%20hands%20for%20additional%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bloem%20Easy%20Pour%20Watering%20Can%C2%A0is%20constructed%20from%20UV-stabilized%20resin%20plastic%20so%20it%20will%20resist%20fading%2C%20warping%2C%20cracking%2C%20and%20freezing.%20The%20material%20is%20also%20FDA-approved%20for%20contact%20with%20food%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20dangerous%20chemicals%20leaching%20into%20the%20water%20you%20give%20to%20your%20vegetable%20patch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20rake%3Cp%3EFor%20many%2C%20a%20rake%20is%20simply%20a%20seasonal%