ay%20of%20this%20cuisine%20is%20characterised%20by%20the%20use%20of%20local%20ingredients%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287953%2Fgurugram-woman-quits-job-odisha-village-sustainable-cooking-practices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%20techniques%2C%20and%20authentic%20flavour%20profiles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20fascinating%20is%20the%20use%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20grains%2C%20lentils%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20spices%2C%20reflecting%20the%20agricultural%20abundance%20of%20their%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20beauty%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20lies%20in%20its%20rich%20diversity.%20While%20the%20recipes%20across%20households%20may%20share%20a%20common%20foundation%2C%20each%20final%20dish%20carries%20its%20own%20unique%20essence.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20hint%20of%20jaggery%20or%20a%20touch%20of%20asafoetida%2C%20perhaps%20some%20zesty%20tamarind%20for%20an%20added%20kick%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20these%20subtle%20variations%20that%20distinguish%20one%20household%E2%80%99s%20creation%20from%20another.%20It%20is%20the%20minute%20intricacies%20like%20the%20proportion%20of%20spices%2C%20duration%2C%20and%20temperature%20of%20roasting%2C%20and%20when%20they%20are%20removed%20from%20the%20flame%2C%20that%20contribute%20to%20robust%20flavours%20that%20infuse%20the%20cuisine%20with%20distinctive%20tastes%2C%20showcasing%20the%20unique%20selling%20point%20of%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244009%2Fviral-trending-america-rasam-tamil-nadu-chef-health-benefits-history-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealmost%20identical%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Esambar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20powders%2C%20every%20household%20crafts%20a%20distinctive%20signature%20flavour%2C%20argues%20Bharat.%20As%20he%20elaborates%20further%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20subtle%20techniques%20and%20personal%20touch%20that%20lend%20an%20edge%20to%20our%20products.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sankethi%20cuisine%20style%20pongal%20(A%20porridge%20made%20using%20rice%2C%20lentils%20and%20spices)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FPongal-Adukale-1710945952-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345384%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPongal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(A%20porridge%20made%20using%20rice%2C%20lentils%20and%20spices)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20June%202019%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EYourStory%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nagarathna%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Adukale%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20guided%20by%20my%20mother-in-law%E2%80%99s%20principles%20when%20it%20came%20to%20cooking.%20The%20ingredients%20would%20be%20freshly%20ground%20and%20powdered%20without%20the%20addition%20of%20any%20preservatives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20about%20what%20these%20principles%20of%20cooking%20were%2C%20Bharat%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283054%2Frnr-donne-biryani-bengaluru-swiggy-zomato-women-entrepreneurs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrandmother%E2%80%99s%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20cooking%2C%20and%20she%20was%20driven%20by%20intuition%20and%20decades%20of%20experience%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20She%20used%20to%20eyeball%20spices%20like%20%3Cem%3Edhaniya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(coriander)%20and%20measure%20it%20by%20a%20fistful%20(she%20had%20a%20small%20fist).%20Spices%20like%20cinnamon%20were%20measured%20by%20the%20length%20of%20her%20fingers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nagaratna%20Ravindra%2C%20co-founder%20and%20director%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FNagaratna-Cofounder-1710946155-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENagaratna%20Ravindra%2C%20co-founder%20and%20director.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBuilding%20on%20her%20foundation%2C%20my%20parents%20then%20added%20some%20methods%20to%20this%20by%20using%20a%20weighing%20scale%20to%20get%20precise%20measurements%20of%20the%20ingredients.%20This%20method%20has%20since%20become%20standardised%20across%20all%20our%20offerings%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20consistently%20deliver%20a%20taste%20that%20resonates%20the%20warmth%20and%20affection%20of%20food%20that%20is%20cooked%20with%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20optimal%20shelf%20life%2C%20Adukale%20claims%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmeticulously%20roast%E2%80%9D%20all%20other%20products%20at%20the%20ideal%20temperature.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%20incorporate%20natural%20preservatives%2C%20such%20as%20salt%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20lemon%2C%20into%20our%20recipes.%20These%20carefully%20chosen%20ingredients%20not%20only%20enhance%20flavour%20profiles%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20prolonging%20the%20freshness%20of%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avarekalu%20uppittu%20(Rava-based%20upma%20using%20hyacinth%20beans).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAvarekalu%20uppittu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rava-based%20%3Cem%3Eupma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eusing%20hyacinth%20beans).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20the%20magic%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20to%20the%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20inception%20%5Bof%20Adukale%5D%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20watch%20my%20parents%20and%20aunt%20bring%20in%20their%20entrepreneurial%20prowess%20and%20passion%20to%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20few%20years%20after%20establishing%20Adukale%2C%20demand%20for%20their%20products%20grew%20so%20extensively%20in%20Bengaluru%20through%20just%20word%20of%20mouth%20that%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20move%20away%20from%20their%20small%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20in%20Malathi%E2%80%99s%20home%20to%20a%203%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2030%20tonnes.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20venture%20shifted%20to%20an%20even%20larger%207%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20in%20South%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20100%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20capacity%20growing%20multi-fold%2C%20their%20processes%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change.%20One%20of%20the%20three%20founding%20partners%20of%20the%20business%20continued%20to%20supervise%20each%20stage%20of%20production%20to%20ensure%20product%20quality%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wane.%20What%20also%20helped%20was%20Bharat%20joining%20the%20business%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWitnessing%20great%20promise%20in%20the%20venture%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20profession%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20the%20US%20to%20join%20Adukale.%20As%20someone%20passionate%20about%20food%20and%20the%20culinary%20landscape%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20in%20my%20global%20experience%20and%20innovation%20to%20scale%20the%20brand%20and%20make%20strides%20in%