20district%20are%20home%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127169%2Fhuman-leopard-conflict-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethriving%20population%20of%20leopards%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20thus%20earning%20the%20area%20this%20moniker.%20The%20ode%20will%20seem%20fitting%20as%20you%20scroll%20through%20the%20scenic%20images%20that%20accompany%20the%20search%20results.%20The%20outlining%20caves%20of%20Jawai%20are%20an%20idyllic%20home%20for%20the%20wild%20cats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20interspersed%20among%20these%20pictures%20%E2%80%94%20some%20that%20showcase%20a%20leopard%20sitting%20idly%2C%20others%20that%20capture%20it%20taking%20a%20stroll%20%E2%80%94%20you%E2%80%99ll%20notice%20a%20few%20surprising%20shots.%20One%20that%20caught%20my%20eye%20was%20a%20leopard%20in%20close%20quarters%20with%20a%20lone%20man%20herding%20his%20cattle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20country%20that%20wakes%20up%20to%20gory%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estories%20of%20leopards%3C%2Fa%3E%20attacking%20and%20mauling%20unfortunate%20humans%2C%20the%20sight%20is%20startling.%20A%20quick%20research%20spree%20led%20me%20to%20discover%20that%20these%20men%20were%20members%20of%20the%20Rabari%20community%20that%20moved%20to%20India%20from%20Iran%20a%20thousand%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20are%20distinguished%20by%20their%20attire%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20a%20red%20turban%20worn%20on%20the%20head%20with%20a%20white%20shirt%20that%20is%20tied%20in%20knots%20with%20strings.%20The%20look%20is%20completed%20with%20a%20floral%20print%20towel%20over%20their%20shoulder%20and%20shoes%20whose%20ends%20curl%20upwards.%20But%20the%20attire%20is%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20this%20nomadic%20pastoral%20community%20is